        <section id="hiw">
            <h1>How we work</h1>
            <section id="hiw-content">
                <article class="hiw">
                    <div class="img"><img src="/icons/assessment.png" alt=""></div>
                    <div class="content">
                        <h4>Needs Assessment</h4>
                        <p >Before taking action, we conduct thorough assessments to understand the specific needs of affected communities. Through on-the-ground surveys, consultations with local authorities, and data analysis, we gather vital information to inform our response efforts.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="hiw">
                    <div class="img"><img src="/icons/emergency.png" alt=""></div>
                    <div class="content">
                        <h4>Emergency Response</h4>
                        <p>In the immediate aftermath of a flood crisis, we swiftly mobilize to provide life-saving aid. This includes distributing emergency supplies such as food, clean water, shelter materials, and medical assistance to those in need. Our teams work tirelessly to reach the most vulnerable populations and ensure no one is left behind.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="hiw">
                    <div class="img"><img src="/icons/long-term.png" alt=""></div>
                    <div class="content">
                        <h4>Long-Term Recovery</h4>
                        <p >Recognizing the lasting impact of floods on communities, we remain committed to supporting long-term recovery efforts. This involves rebuilding infrastructure, restoring livelihoods, providing psychosocial support, and implementing disaster risk reduction measures to enhance resilience against future disasters.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="hiw">
                    <div class="img"><img src="/icons/accountability.png" alt=""></div>
                    <div class="content">
                        <h4>Transparency and Accountability</h4>
                        <p >Transparency is at the core of our operations. We uphold the highest standards of accountability, providing regular updates, financial reports, and impact assessments to our donors and stakeholders. We believe in building trust through openness and honesty in all our dealings.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="hiw">
                    <div class="img"><img src="/icons/collaboration.png" alt=""></div>
                    <div class="content">
                        <h4>Collaboration</h4>
                        <p >We understand the importance of collaboration in achieving meaningful impact. We forge partnerships with local organizations, governments, and other stakeholders to leverage resources, share expertise, and coordinate efforts effectively. Together, we amplify our collective impact and maximize support for flood-affected communities.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="hiw">
                    <div class="img"><img src="/icons/volunteer.png" alt=""></div>
